text: Laura Cox is an American water polo player. She was a member of the United States women's national water polo team. She played at the 1979 FINA World Cup and 1981 World Games. She played for University of California, Santa Barbara's women's water polo team. == References == == Other websites == * https://twitter.com/USAWP/status/1220527383603601408 Category:Living people Category:American water polo players Category:1961 births
